                <h4>Chippy</h4><p>关键词：弹幕射击</p><p>发售日期：6月15日</p><p>在弹幕中面对巨型像素 boss！通过射击将 boss 的不同区块解体，击破 boss 的核心来获得胜利！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Chippy0984Yx.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13756" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/602700/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Project Arrhythmia</h4><p>关键词：音乐、动作</p><p>发售日期：6月15日</p><p>喔！这可不是 Just Shapes &amp; Beats！实际上这款在 JSaB 推出之前就在开发中啦~本作同样是很棒的音乐动作弹幕游戏，同时还有关卡编辑器+丰富的社区关卡库！游戏最多支持8人合作游玩。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Project_Arrhythmia13676Kq.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13757" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Project_Arrhythmia23689F8.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13758" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Project_Arrhythmia5498qn.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13759" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/440310/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Speakerman</h4><p>关键词：冒险、探索</p><p>发售日期：6月17日</p><p>分为故事、开放世界两个模式。如果你喜欢寻找地图上的隐藏区域、不可见的平台和一些有点哲学气息的角色对话，本作值得一试。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Speakerman15739h7.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13760" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Speakerman26077fM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13761" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Speakerman36084n2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13762" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1089050/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Littlewood</h4><p>关键词：冒险、种田、收集</p><p>发售日期：6月18日（EA）</p><p>你打败了黑暗巫师！世界重回和平，但你却忘记付出了什么代价。作为救世英雄，在你的城镇中开展新生活吧！定制城市、种地、采矿、钓鱼、制作，探索森林和洞穴，与来到镇上的旅者交流以寻回你尘封的记忆。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Littlewood16781S2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13763" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Littlewood26789sU.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13764" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/894940/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>A.N.N.E</h4><p>关键词：RPG、平台冒险、飞行射击</p><p>发售日期：6月18日（EA）</p><p>被感染了“爱”之病毒的机器人都被流放至遥远的冰封星球上进行拆解，终于你的幸运也走到了尽头。但一场小行星雨妨碍了联邦舰队的追击，现在就是救出恋人 A.N.N.E 并逃走的时机！</p><p>徒步或者借助小飞行器探索世界，收集被拆解同伴的零件，定制你的武器能力。用你的飞船对抗星球的强大守卫！游戏也额外提供了自动瞄准及休闲模式，不用为闯关挫败感担心，享受探索像素世界的乐趣吧！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-ANNE75387X.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13766" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-ANNE27545ys.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13767" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-ANNE37551Da.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13768" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/262370/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Chook &amp; Sosig: Walk the Plank</h4><p>关键词：点击、可爱</p><p>发售日期：6月18日</p><p>和可爱的朋友们一起穿上不同的服装，扮演海盗，寻找传说中的宝藏！多个结局分支可供选择，游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Chook_&amp;_Sosig186910m.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13769" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Chook_&amp;_Sosig38716JF.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13770" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Chook_&amp;_Sosig28723ET.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13771" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/899470/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Failed State</h4><p>关键词：动作、冒险</p><p>发售日期：6月20日</p><p>各种天灾让人类文明已奄奄一息，Rose 在这个末日后世界中，骑上机车四处搜刮资源以求生存。面对形形色色的人们，Rose 总要做出不同的选择，有时必须以武力相对。探索废弃的楼房，撬锁搜集资源素材，制作武器道具，同时防御劫匪和未知的黑暗生物。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Failed_State105859V.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13772" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Failed_State20597p5.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13773" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Failed_State30604jk.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13774" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/409350/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>My Friend Pedro</h4><p>关键词：动作、子弹时间、跑酷</p><p>发售日期：6月21日</p><p>详细介绍：<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/my-friend-pedro-blood-bullets-bananas-preview/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《慢动作，有多酷？》</a></p><p>人挡杀人、佛挡杀佛！滑索、翻滚、破窗而入，大杀四方！游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-My_Friend_Pedro12175XS.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13775" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-My_Friend_Pedro22198zi.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13776" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/557340/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>198X</h4><p>关键词：怀旧、街机、叙事</p><p>发售日期：6月21日</p><p>198X 年，一名少年为年少的局限性及成年后的责任而不断烦恼。镇上的街机厅成为他排解烦恼的好去处，每当他发现一款新游戏，每精通一个招式，每打败一个 boss，少年也变得越发强大。游戏世界与现实世界的边界似乎越来越模糊……</p><p>游戏由多个不同玩法的街机游戏组成，目前放出的是本作的第一章，时长约2小时，暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-198X12469Hh.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13777" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-198X22476l9.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13778" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-198X32485Eq.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13779" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1086010/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Meowk and Frocco</h4><p>关键词：休闲、动作</p><p>发售日期：6月21日</p><p>你的火箭坠毁了，只有喷气背包才能帮助你在失重环境中移动。闯过层层关卡，找到自己失踪的好友！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Meowk_and_Frocco4029Z1.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13780" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1088110/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Ritbone</h4><p>关键词：平台、冒险</p><p>发售日期：6月21日</p><p>进入地下世界拯救自己的泰迪熊！丰富的平台跳跃关卡和谜题等着你来挑战。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Ritbone144536d.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13781" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Ritbone244627w.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13782" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1084880/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Grab Lab</h4><p>关键词：动作、休闲</p><p>发售日期：6月22日</p><p>利用异常的重力和钩锁收集药水，修好故障的时间机器和一团糟的实验室！<br><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Grab_Lab6876wG.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13783" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1001590/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Seen</h4><p>关键词：横轴奔跑</p><p>发售日期：6月22日</p><p>一个孤独的孩子，拼命逃离他的黑暗回忆。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Seen17403iX.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13784" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Seen27412gV.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13785" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Seen3741780.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13786" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1069740/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Data Defense</h4><p>关键词：策略、塔防</p><p>发售日期：6月22日</p><p>保护数据服务器，防御故障、错误及病毒！对于不同的服务器布局，使用30多种模块组合闯过50+个关卡。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/06/pic-Data_Defense8040F2.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="13787" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/812650/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>本周其他值得关注的作品</h4><ul><li>编程解谜游戏开发组 Zachtronics 的游戏设计手稿<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1098840/ZACHLIKE/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《ZACH-LIKE》电子书</a>（和一些小游戏原型，免费下载）</li><li>VR 短片 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1093330/Conscious_Existence__A_Journey_Within/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Conscious Existence - A Journey Within</a></li><li>恶魔城精神续作<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/692850/Bloodstained_Ritual_of_the_Night/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《赤痕·：夜之仪式》</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/919640/Steel_Division_2/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《钢铁雄师2》</a></li><li>《囧魂》开发组的 RPG 新作<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/965820/_Things_as_They_Are/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《沉睡的法则 Things as They Are》</a></li><li>战棋卡牌 roguelike 游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1017410/Tetra_Project/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《原石计划》demo</a></li><li>电竞战队模拟经营游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/897410/Esports_Life_Tycoon/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Esports Life Tycoon</a></li><li>以老彼得·布吕赫尔的画作《儿童游戏》为蓝本的 VR 寻物游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071310/1_2_3_Bruegel/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">1, 2, 3... Bruegel!</a></li><li>VR 体验莫奈的睡莲花园 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1071170/Claude_Monet__The_Water_Lily_obsession/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Claude Monet - The Water Lily obsession</a></li><li>网易的 VR 西部多人在线射击游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/978180/Stay_Silent/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Stay Silent</a></li><li>为了升级电脑配置而抢劫 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1099840/1000/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">1000$</a></li><li>勇者海王星 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1016960/Super_Neptunia_RPG/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Super Neptunia RPG</a></li><li>免费未来科幻 FPS <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/783770/Ironsight_PreOBT_ver/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Ironsight</a></li></ul>
